                  <!--  *************************************  <decoDesc>  *********************************     -->
                  <decoDesc>
                     <decoNote>
                        <p>Wheel made Castor Ware jug; pinkish clay; dull black glaze; details in
                           white and orange. Narrow base; globular body; conical neck; moulded rim;
                           raised ridge at junction of neck and body; two lines of rouletting and
                           one incised groove around the body. Wavy white ridge just above the first
                           line of rouletting; white dots on the second line of rouletting, and on
                           the incised groove; wider band of scrolls and bunches of grapes in relief
                           below the inscription.</p>
                     </decoNote>
                  </decoDesc>
